Package csc1035.project2

Class User_Room

java.lang.Object
csc1035.project2.User_Room
All Implemented Interfaces:
IUser_Room
@Entity
public class User_Room
extends java.lang.Object
implements IUser_Room
This object acts as a table of reservations. It is the join table between User and Rooms to model the many to many connection with composite key containing additional attributes between them. It has method making reservations or canceling them and showing the available room in a given datetime and duration.
